{"tid":955982,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[你們的女神］富家女簡淑兒好慳家 攻平價貨兼研究贈品","createTime":"2018-12-26T01:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T08:35:19.000Z","uid":12558,"like":4,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"25bdd1da851999badec144287c25d124ad88716f","tid":955982,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T01:36:57.000Z","msg":"簡淑兒和陳婉衡，一個走可愛路線，一個走性感型格路線，想不到兩人原來是朋友。這天他們二人個再加上一個友人一起在銅鑼灣逛街。經過愛護動物拹會擺的攤位，她們停下左挑右選，最後簡淑兒買了頂帽子，支持公益。幾個女人逛街，就當然是看衣服，不過一行三人進的都是平價連鎖店。風格不同，看的衣服果然是南轅北轍。陳婉衡一進店內，就拿起一條性感貼身背心短裙拼在身上，而簡淑兒就在看粉藍色荷葉的露肩衣。逛完一會沒甚麼心水。她們就去了萬寧，三個女生站在贈品牌前不斷研究，想不到傳聞有點家底，小時候就移民美國，家裡做珠寶生意的簡淑兒都會對萬寧的贈品那麼有興趣。女生當然愛美，為了把髮型用好，陳婉衡開了手機鏡頭讓簡淑兒當鏡子照。始終作為女藝人，儀容很重要！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vYYfjZS9ZGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvYYfjZS9ZGQ&d=VEnvoTX589ayptzzh3AaWU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=537cf0e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vYYfjZS9ZGQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KPAsmtw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKPAsmtw.png&h=cced0d56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YcrK78w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYcrK78w.png&h=960cdc49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XSn2UOx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXSn2UOx.png&h=18f774e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hq4kGty.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHq4kGty.png&h=3b4de8bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9959af05c2265293113f2ee541141559c14be75b","tid":955982,"uid":122601,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T01:38:24.000Z","msg":"膠 娃娃樣咁"},{"pid":"18ce4a754fc80e1f2f0e79dbf2459c7aafa69af3","tid":955982,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T01:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif